 | [_ck_]: cfw-calendar             | ^^                                  |
 | [_cc_]: Org: capture             | [_go_]: Helm: my org files          |
 | [_oa_]: Org: agenda: life        | [_gs_]: Helm: my local/web shortcuts|
 | [_oA_]: Org: agenda: work        | ^^                                  |
